      <title>现货以太币 ETF 有望最早于下周开始交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/spot-ether-etfs-are-seen-starting-to-trade-as-early-as-next-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，美国证券交易委员会已指示至少四家现货以太币交易所交易基金的发行人提交文件以获得可能的批准。其中三家发行人表示，该机构暗示交易可能于 7 月 23 日开始。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/spot-ether-etfs-are-seen-starting-to-trade-as-early-as-next-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 16:47:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
